       - type: apiKey Authorization (HEADER)
       - name: GatewayLogin
     - API Key:
       - type: apiKey DirectLogin (HEADER)
       - name: DirectLogin
     - parameter implicit: (path) The IMPLICIT identifier 
     - parameter createConsentImplicitRequest: (body) Request body 
